A PCB based solution having ATmega-16 microcontroller which involve the following features:-
    1. 4 x 4 Keypad interfacing.
    2. The 4 x 4 keypad should be able to generate 10 numbers (0-9) and 26 characters (a-z).
    3. LCD to display message to be transmitted or received.
    4. Transmission and reception of message via Bluetooth.
